By":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:42:34.000Z","msg":"聲波好定 旋轉頭好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"早幾日行過萬寧見到呢支聲波，未試過旋轉刷牙<br />\n但試曬旋轉同聲波好似呢個馬力勁d就買佢<br />\n加埋佢支美白牙膏買左黎試<br />\n排牙白左好多，乾淨好睇左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似舒服版既洗牙咁，唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNGpR0s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNGpR0s.png&h=3a747837&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}